s.from_options()` maps CLI dict correctly\n477: 10. ✅ `PackRuntime` integrates with `MetadataService`\n478: 11. ✅ `StatusRuntime` exported in `agentcube.__all__`\n479: 12. ✅ Unit tests cover all validators and methods (>= 80% coverage)\n480: 13. ✅ Integration tests verify full pack workflow\n481: 14. ✅ Docstrings follow Google/NumPy style conventions\n482: 15. ✅ Type hints pass mypy validation\n483: 16. ✅ Example `agent_metadata.yaml` provided\n484: \n485: ---\n486: \n487: **Notes:**\n488: - Stage ST-3 marked complete per design.md\n489: - Core implementation (metadata_service.py) exists and is functional\n490: - Tests exist in test_metadata_service.py (7 tests)\n491: - Remaining work: MetadataOptions, PackRuntime integration, exports, expanded tests, documentation\n\n(End of file - total 491 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\n\n**Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model Implementation\n\n- [x] **T1.1** Define `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `metadata_service.py`\n  - Import `BaseModel`, `Field`, `field_validator` from pydantic\n  - Add `from __future__ import annotations` for type hints\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verify: Model class defined with proper inheritance\n\n- [x] **T1.2** Implement core identification fields\n  - `agent_name: str` (required)\n  - `description: Optional[str]` (default None)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875146367,"end":1775875146422}}}}
