{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875290619,"sessionID":"ses_28597ee40ffedwHk3wDZsgmjO5","part":{"id":"prt_d7a68add0001fiiSCXKhxQ7fzC","messageID":"msg_d7a68a2f70010KuM2DVavPH717","sessionID":"ses_28597ee40ffedwHk3wDZsgmjO5","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_2a1d5a620841473c85446680","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","content":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Package Structure & Exceptions ✓\n\n- [x] **T1.1** Create `agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Import `CodeInterpreterClient` from `code_interpreter`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeClient` from `agent_runtime`\n  - Define `__all__ = [\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Verify: `from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient` works\n\n- [x] **T1.2** Create `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Define `AgentCubeError(Exception)` base class\n  - Define `CommandExecutionError(AgentCubeError)` with `exit_code`, `stderr`, `command` attributes\n  - Define `SessionError(AgentCubeError)` placeholder\n  - Define `DataPlaneError(AgentCubeError)` placeholder\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - Verify: All exception classes instantiate correctly\n\n- [x] **T1.3** Create `agentcube/utils/__init__.py`\n  - Empty file (module marker)\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/__init__.py`\n  - Verify: Module imports successfully\n\n- [x] **T1.4** Create `agentcube/utils/http.py`\n  - Import `requests`\n  - Implement `create_session(pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)`\n  - Mount `HTTPAdapter` for `http://` and `https://`\n  - Return configured `requests.Session`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n  - Verify: Session has adapters mounted for http/https\n\n- [x]